@startuml Data Analysis Use Cases
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam linetype ortho

title Smart X-Ray Screening - Data Analysis Use Cases

' ============ ACTORS ============
actor "Data Scientist/\nML Engineer" as DataScientist #LightGreen

' ============ SYSTEM BOUNDARY ============
rectangle "Data Analysis System" {
  
  usecase "Analyze Patient Demographics" as UC1
  usecase "Analyze Disease Patterns" as UC2
  usecase "Analyze Bounding Box Data" as UC3
  usecase "Load Dataset CSV" as UC4
  usecase "Process Image Metadata" as UC5
  usecase "Calculate Statistics" as UC6
  usecase "Generate Visualizations" as UC7
  usecase "Export Analysis Results" as UC8
}

' ============ RELATIONSHIPS ============

DataScientist --> UC1
DataScientist --> UC2
DataScientist --> UC3

' Analysis flow
UC1 ..> UC4 : <<include>>
UC2 ..> UC4 : <<include>>
UC3 ..> UC4 : <<include>>

UC1 ..> UC5 : <<include>>
UC2 ..> UC5 : <<include>>

UC1 ..> UC6 : <<include>>
UC2 ..> UC6 : <<include>>
UC3 ..> UC6 : <<include>>

UC6 ..> UC7 : <<include>>
UC7 ..> UC8 : <<extend>>

' ============ NOTES ============
note top of UC1
  **Demographics Analysis:**
  - Age distribution
  - Gender patterns
  - View position frequency
end note

note right of UC2
  **Disease Analysis:**
  - Disease co-occurrence
  - Disease prevalence
  - Correlation patterns
end note

note top of UC3
  **Bounding Box Analysis:**
  - Spatial distribution
  - Box size statistics
  - Location patterns
end note

note bottom of UC7
  **Visualization Types:**
  - Bar plots
  - Scatter plots
  - Histograms
  - Heatmaps
  - Distribution charts
end note

legend bottom
  |= Relationship |= Description |
  | ──> | Actor initiates |
  | ..> <<include>> | Required step |
  | ..> <<extend>> | Optional step |
  
  **Data Sources:**
  - Data_Entry_2017_v2020.csv
  - BBox_List_2017.csv
endlegend

@enduml
